WEBVTT

00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:20.940
=About Love=

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.940
=Episode 20=

00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:25.480
Mom.

00:01:27.120 --> 00:01:29.350
I'm bringing my boyfriend Bei to see you

00:01:29.350 --> 00:01:30.350
in a couple of days.

00:01:30.510 --> 00:01:31.590
Get ready.

00:01:32.640 --> 00:01:34.350
I've been waiting for this day.

00:01:34.590 --> 00:01:37.200
I'm curious what kind of guy

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:39.510
could make my picky daughter
so satisfied.

00:01:39.790 --> 00:01:41.150
I'm not picky.

00:01:41.150 --> 00:01:42.400
Don't make it sound like that.

00:01:42.950 --> 00:01:45.590
Not picky? You've been single for years.

00:01:46.340 --> 00:01:47.200
By the way,

00:01:47.200 --> 00:01:48.560
your dad happens to be heading your way.

00:01:48.840 --> 00:01:50.590
I asked your dad to check him out first.

00:01:50.920 --> 00:01:51.760
Dad's here?

00:01:52.790 --> 00:01:53.950
When did he arrive?

00:01:54.230 --> 00:01:55.430
Why didn't he call me?

00:01:55.710 --> 00:01:56.840
He's on a business trip.

00:01:56.840 --> 00:01:58.200
I told him to stop by after he's done.

00:01:58.560 --> 00:02:01.040
Didn't tell you in advance
because I didn't want you to worry.

00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:02.870
Didn't want to trouble you.

00:02:19.750 --> 00:02:21.150
Jiang Yifan is Jiang Yifan.

00:02:22.750 --> 00:02:24.770
Jiang Yifan will never be Li Xiaoxi.

00:02:24.870 --> 00:02:26.910
What I liked
was just a made-up character.

00:02:33.560 --> 00:02:34.800
Mm, got it.

00:02:36.630 --> 00:02:38.080
Alright, hanging up. Bye bye.

00:02:39.430 --> 00:02:40.960
What's wrong? A call from home?

00:02:40.960 --> 00:02:41.800
Mm.

00:02:43.240 --> 00:02:44.590
Mom said my dad's here

00:02:45.030 --> 00:02:45.870
on a business trip.

00:02:46.520 --> 00:02:48.280
I asked him to dinner tomorrow night.

00:02:48.280 --> 00:02:49.240
You coming?

00:02:49.240 --> 00:02:50.190
Of course.

00:02:51.040 --> 00:02:52.280
Why don't I book the restaurant?

00:02:52.720 --> 00:02:53.800
What does your dad like to eat?

00:02:54.910 --> 00:02:55.800
How about...

00:02:55.800 --> 00:02:56.750
Sichuan food?

00:02:57.800 --> 00:02:58.640
Forget it.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:00.240
Your family always eats Sichuan food.

00:03:00.240 --> 00:03:01.080
- You're...
- Western...

00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:02.910
Are you feeling a bit nervous?

00:03:02.910 --> 00:03:05.120
Me? Nervous about what? I'm not nervous.

00:03:05.120 --> 00:03:05.960
Where's my phone?

00:03:05.960 --> 00:03:06.870
I'm not nervous.

00:03:06.870 --> 00:03:08.590
You're nervous. You are.

00:03:08.590 --> 00:03:10.520
I'm not. Why would I be nervous?

00:03:10.870 --> 00:03:12.000
Wait, my phone's here.

00:03:12.240 --> 00:03:13.150
So…

00:03:13.150 --> 00:03:14.360
When's your dad heading back?

00:03:14.360 --> 00:03:15.560
Should I prepare something?

00:03:15.560 --> 00:03:16.960
Going back with your dad,

00:03:17.150 --> 00:03:18.150
and meet aunt then.

00:03:19.190 --> 00:03:20.120
Just say hello.

00:03:20.120 --> 00:03:20.960
What's the rush?

00:03:21.400 --> 00:03:22.470
I'm not rushing.

00:03:23.100 --> 00:03:25.000
You're in such a hurry.
I need to think carefully.

00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:26.870
Should I think it over some more?

00:03:27.910 --> 00:03:29.520
You really should.

00:03:29.600 --> 00:03:30.710
I'll give you three seconds.

00:03:31.080 --> 00:03:32.590
Three, two...

00:03:32.960 --> 00:03:33.800
Okay!

00:03:34.240 --> 00:03:35.080
That was fast.

00:03:36.400 --> 00:03:37.910
You really thought hard about it.

00:03:44.030 --> 00:03:45.910
Since you've thought it through
so carefully,

00:03:46.680 --> 00:03:47.800
promise me one thing.

00:03:49.120 --> 00:03:49.960
What is it?

00:03:54.030 --> 00:03:55.000
Don't leave me.

00:04:00.240 --> 00:04:01.080
I promise.

00:04:04.360 --> 00:04:05.200
Deal.

00:04:22.950 --> 00:04:25.720
We used to drink like this all the time.

00:04:28.120 --> 00:04:29.920
Why did we break up?

00:04:33.430 --> 00:04:35.190
How much did you drink already?

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:37.630
Don't play dumb
just because you're tipsy.

00:04:42.270 --> 00:04:43.600
Well, I...

00:04:44.510 --> 00:04:48.160
liked you so, so much.

00:04:49.950 --> 00:04:52.070
Why would I leave you?

00:04:53.750 --> 00:04:55.270
Because I'm a jerk.

00:04:55.800 --> 00:04:56.830
I fell for someone else.

00:04:58.390 --> 00:04:59.270
That's not true.

00:05:00.270 --> 00:05:01.110
I know

00:05:02.270 --> 00:05:04.310
you're mad at me.

00:05:05.310 --> 00:05:07.720
Mad because I don't trust you.

00:05:09.800 --> 00:05:11.160
And even had someone test you.

00:05:15.950 --> 00:05:17.120
So you knew all along?

00:05:19.510 --> 00:05:20.510
It's one of the reasons.

00:05:26.560 --> 00:05:27.600
I didn't want to.

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:30.070
But I…

00:05:30.560 --> 00:05:31.830
When I started thinking about

00:05:31.830 --> 00:05:33.160
how many women

00:05:33.160 --> 00:05:34.830
you might be chatting with
on your phone,

00:05:34.830 --> 00:05:36.560
I just couldn't help it.

00:05:39.750 --> 00:05:42.630
If you like me, can't you stay loyal?

00:05:44.160 --> 00:05:46.430
Do you remember what you told me before?

00:05:47.310 --> 00:05:48.310
You said,

00:05:49.430 --> 00:05:50.360
"Yu He,

00:05:50.950 --> 00:05:51.790
don't worry.

00:05:53.600 --> 00:05:55.240
I'll never hurt you."

00:05:56.600 --> 00:05:58.360
Total nonsense.

00:06:01.120 --> 00:06:02.360
In this world,

00:06:03.190 --> 00:06:04.680
the one who hurt me the most

00:06:07.510 --> 00:06:08.350
is you.

00:06:15.360 --> 00:06:16.310
To...

00:06:17.560 --> 00:06:18.630
stop hurting you,

00:06:23.310 --> 00:06:24.560
so I left.

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:26.950
How could you say

00:06:26.950 --> 00:06:29.000
something so awful?

00:06:29.870 --> 00:06:32.510
You shouldn't have come to me
in the first place.

00:06:45.040 --> 00:06:47.190
Back when we first got together,

00:06:49.120 --> 00:06:50.310
you were like a doll.

00:06:54.070 --> 00:06:55.830
More like an angel.

00:06:57.800 --> 00:06:58.950
You had wings.

00:07:01.190 --> 00:07:02.720
You loved circling around me,

00:07:03.360 --> 00:07:04.200
hovering here

00:07:05.480 --> 00:07:06.320
and there.

00:07:21.270 --> 00:07:22.750
But as time went on,

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:26.480
those wings disappeared.

00:07:32.240 --> 00:07:33.800
Knew there'd be a catch.

00:07:44.190 --> 00:07:45.120
You'd

00:07:46.390 --> 00:07:48.870
always cling to my arm

00:07:49.830 --> 00:07:50.670
and my leg.

00:07:51.190 --> 00:07:52.750
Sometimes you cling onto my back

00:07:52.920 --> 00:07:54.360
like a koala,

00:07:56.600 --> 00:07:58.270
weighing me down

00:07:59.630 --> 00:08:02.310
heavier and heavier,

00:08:02.800 --> 00:08:03.830
until I can barely breathe.

00:08:03.830 --> 00:08:04.670
Let me see.

00:08:04.950 --> 00:08:06.920
What's there to see? Are you a kid?

00:08:06.920 --> 00:08:07.870
Let me take a look.

00:08:07.870 --> 00:08:08.830
Am I your girlfriend

00:08:08.830 --> 00:08:10.190
or is she?

00:08:10.190 --> 00:08:11.030
What right does she have?

00:08:11.040 --> 00:08:12.630
If I tried to put you down,

00:08:13.190 --> 00:08:14.120
or

00:08:14.120 --> 00:08:17.360
tried to talk to other women,

00:08:17.750 --> 00:08:18.750
you'd let out

00:08:19.360 --> 00:08:20.950
shrill screams.

00:08:24.480 --> 00:08:26.070
Do you dislike me that much?

00:08:26.920 --> 00:08:28.360
It's not that I dislike you.

00:08:30.750 --> 00:08:32.030
I just feel

00:08:34.960 --> 00:08:35.870
a bit tired.

00:08:40.360 --> 00:08:42.030
I just joked with your bestie,

00:08:42.030 --> 00:08:43.150
and you got mad about it.

00:08:43.550 --> 00:08:46.000
You even suspected something
between me and Luanluan.

00:08:49.750 --> 00:08:52.240
Am I not allowed to have female friends?

00:08:53.320 --> 00:08:54.480
You went out of your way,

00:08:54.480 --> 00:08:56.030
racked your brain

00:08:56.510 --> 00:08:59.240
to find proof that I was unfaithful.

00:09:00.120 --> 00:09:01.120
Did you find any?

00:09:04.200 --> 00:09:05.120
Congrats,

00:09:06.240 --> 00:09:07.320
you finally succeeded.

00:09:15.270 --> 00:09:16.270
But...

00:09:19.000 --> 00:09:21.360
when you like someone,

00:09:21.910 --> 00:09:23.360
you just get insecure.

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:28.440
If you think Li Xiaoxi's great,

00:09:28.790 --> 00:09:30.440
then go be with her.

00:09:31.150 --> 00:09:32.960
See if you don't drive her nuts.

00:09:34.750 --> 00:09:35.630
Wait.

00:09:35.790 --> 00:09:36.840
Wait, that's not right.

00:09:40.120 --> 00:09:41.720
She doesn't even like you.

00:09:42.840 --> 00:09:44.870
She doesn't even care

00:09:45.150 --> 00:09:45.990
how many

00:09:46.390 --> 00:09:48.720
close female friends you have.

00:09:54.270 --> 00:09:55.670
Enough.

00:09:56.080 --> 00:09:58.360
She's getting married. Why bring her up?

00:10:01.240 --> 00:10:02.120
Wait.

00:10:03.670 --> 00:10:05.630
She's marrying Bei?

00:10:06.840 --> 00:10:07.870
That fast?

00:10:12.550 --> 00:10:13.390
Thank goodness.

00:10:13.960 --> 00:10:15.000
Thank goodness.

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:17.150
Lucky she didn't end up with you.

00:10:17.150 --> 00:10:17.990
Otherwise,

00:10:19.550 --> 00:10:21.960
she'd never have gotten a happy ending.

00:10:27.320 --> 00:10:28.960
Are you here to insult me?

00:10:29.600 --> 00:10:33.270
You told me they're getting married.

00:10:36.720 --> 00:10:37.910
Struck a nerve, huh?

00:10:40.030 --> 00:10:41.870
Yeah, I am here to insult you.

00:10:43.030 --> 00:10:44.720
And I'm gonna scold you.

00:10:46.120 --> 00:10:48.670
I dislike you, hate you,

00:10:49.270 --> 00:10:50.240
and resent you.

00:10:51.390 --> 00:10:53.870
I'll do whatever it takes
to get back at you.

00:10:53.870 --> 00:10:55.790
I want you

00:10:55.790 --> 00:10:57.840
to never be with someone you like.

00:11:03.150 --> 00:11:04.670
I can't stop thinking about you.

00:11:33.360 --> 00:11:34.200
What's wrong?

00:11:42.910 --> 00:11:44.870
I don't want to hurt you again.

00:11:50.440 --> 00:11:52.120
Are you afraid I'll cling to you?

00:11:54.390 --> 00:11:56.360
Actually, I was about to...

00:11:58.360 --> 00:11:59.440
get married.

00:12:04.270 --> 00:12:05.110
Well...

00:12:06.790 --> 00:12:07.630
You...

00:12:08.840 --> 00:12:09.750
Did you take me as

00:12:09.910 --> 00:12:11.440
your last wild night before marriage?

00:12:13.720 --> 00:12:14.560
I...

00:12:15.790 --> 00:12:18.240
I follow the rules and have principles.

00:12:18.550 --> 00:12:19.440
I'm a decent person.

00:12:30.480 --> 00:12:32.720
Let me tell you, I've

00:12:32.720 --> 00:12:35.120
imagined so many times

00:12:35.120 --> 00:12:36.320
how you'd react

00:12:36.320 --> 00:12:37.550
when you heard the news.

00:12:38.000 --> 00:12:40.000
Would you be even a little

00:12:41.080 --> 00:12:43.720
bit sad?

00:12:44.120 --> 00:12:45.270
Or

00:12:45.550 --> 00:12:46.390
regretful?

00:12:49.200 --> 00:12:50.200
Thanks.

00:12:51.320 --> 00:12:53.510
Thanks for letting me know
I was overthinking.

00:12:57.840 --> 00:12:58.870
Congrats.

00:13:00.720 --> 00:13:01.750
That guy

00:13:02.400 --> 00:13:03.670
must be more reliable than me.

00:13:05.390 --> 00:13:06.230
T...

00:13:06.360 --> 00:13:08.320
Today's full of good news.

00:13:08.810 --> 00:13:09.750
Just pretend it didn't...

00:13:09.750 --> 00:13:12.200
He discussed home renovation with me

00:13:13.030 --> 00:13:14.670
and brainstormed

00:13:14.670 --> 00:13:16.840
baby names with me.

00:13:17.550 --> 00:13:19.750
He made so many plans

00:13:19.750 --> 00:13:20.960
for the future with me.

00:13:22.440 --> 00:13:24.120
You must think it's silly.

00:13:26.150 --> 00:13:28.080
Because you never talk to me about that.

00:13:29.910 --> 00:13:31.120
In your future,

00:13:33.150 --> 00:13:34.480
I'm nowhere to be found.

00:13:38.240 --> 00:13:39.510
You know me.

00:13:41.720 --> 00:13:43.750
I live for the moment.

00:13:46.240 --> 00:13:48.120
When he proposed to me,

00:13:49.630 --> 00:13:51.550
all I could think about was you.

00:13:53.030 --> 00:13:54.720
I just wanted you to know

00:13:55.910 --> 00:13:58.360
someone wanted to marry me.

00:13:59.910 --> 00:14:01.150
But then I backed out.

00:14:03.510 --> 00:14:04.720
I got scared again.

00:14:07.390 --> 00:14:10.080
I was wondering if I was really
ready to marry this person.

00:14:14.270 --> 00:14:15.360
I wasn't sure.

00:14:16.630 --> 00:14:19.080
I couldn't marry him
with that thought in my heart.

00:14:19.080 --> 00:14:20.030
So I told him

00:14:22.150 --> 00:14:23.910
I still haven't completely let you go.

00:14:24.220 --> 00:14:26.260
♪I'll stay insane♪

00:14:26.620 --> 00:14:29.290
♪When you call my name♪

00:14:29.630 --> 00:14:31.910
I came today
because I wanted to see you.

00:14:33.100 --> 00:14:35.120
Until the moment
you were getting out of the car,

00:14:35.120 --> 00:14:36.840
I still didn't know
how to start talking.

00:14:39.720 --> 00:14:40.910
But luckily,

00:14:41.600 --> 00:14:43.670
luckily you mentioned

00:14:43.670 --> 00:14:46.030
the comic adaptation.

00:14:47.200 --> 00:14:48.120
You have no idea

00:14:48.720 --> 00:14:49.790
how happy I was

00:14:50.510 --> 00:14:51.600
in that moment.

00:14:54.440 --> 00:14:55.330
It's all in the past.

00:14:55.330 --> 00:14:57.000
♪At night♪

00:14:57.000 --> 00:14:59.880
♪I wonder if it will go away♪

00:15:00.030 --> 00:15:01.390
Is there any chance for us?

00:15:02.970 --> 00:15:04.710
♪At dawn♪

00:15:06.750 --> 00:15:07.720
I'm...

00:15:09.080 --> 00:15:10.270
still that jerk.

00:15:12.000 --> 00:15:13.870
We can't make the same mistake twice.

00:15:18.130 --> 00:15:21.500
♪Thinking about how to stay the same♪

00:15:21.670 --> 00:15:23.550
The second time isn't a mistake.

00:15:26.240 --> 00:15:27.150
It's a choice.

00:15:27.150 --> 00:15:31.980
♪I lie awake♪

00:15:32.000 --> 00:15:33.480
I already know what you've chosen.

00:15:34.180 --> 00:15:37.860
♪Thinking there's nothing I could say♪

00:15:38.240 --> 00:15:42.310
♪Only to lie and lie awake♪

00:15:43.670 --> 00:15:44.600
I'm sorry.

00:15:48.080 --> 00:15:49.480
I never meant to hurt you.

00:15:51.030 --> 00:15:51.870
You know what?

00:16:03.120 --> 00:16:03.960
Yu He.

00:16:16.890 --> 00:16:18.860
♪At night♪

00:16:19.030 --> 00:16:23.630
♪I wonder if it will go away♪

00:16:24.690 --> 00:16:26.970
♪At dawn♪

00:16:26.970 --> 00:16:31.620
♪I wonder if I will be okay♪

00:16:32.860 --> 00:16:39.860
♪I lie awake♪

00:16:40.140 --> 00:16:44.060
♪Thinking there's nothing I could say♪

00:16:44.230 --> 00:16:48.550
♪Only to lie and lie awake♪

00:16:53.960 --> 00:16:55.080
What's this?

00:16:56.270 --> 00:16:57.440
It's a music box.

00:16:58.080 --> 00:16:59.320
It's the little princess.

00:17:00.600 --> 00:17:02.870
It's a dancing little princess.

00:17:03.750 --> 00:17:04.640
Do you like it?

00:17:04.880 --> 00:17:05.720
I do.

00:17:06.070 --> 00:17:07.310
Thank you, Dad.

00:17:10.680 --> 00:17:11.880
It's really beautiful.

00:17:16.640 --> 00:17:17.480
No.

00:17:17.790 --> 00:17:18.960
He's not your dad.

00:17:19.640 --> 00:17:20.480
He's not.

00:17:49.400 --> 00:17:50.270
(Uncle)
(Sen)

00:17:50.270 --> 00:17:52.110
(Can you stop worrying the family?)

00:17:52.350 --> 00:17:53.680
(Break up with her.)

00:17:54.340 --> 00:17:56.540
(Aunt)

00:17:57.110 --> 00:17:58.310
(Text)
(Have you lost your mind?)

00:17:58.440 --> 00:17:59.960
(She's a homewrecker.)

00:17:59.960 --> 00:18:01.160
(And you still want to be with her?)

00:18:01.640 --> 00:18:02.550
(Take my advice.)

00:18:02.830 --> 00:18:03.880
(End it quickly.)

00:18:22.640 --> 00:18:25.510
(Dad)
(We all disagree. Break up now.)

00:18:25.830 --> 00:18:27.590
(You've embarrassed us all.)

00:18:49.480 --> 00:18:50.480
Where am I?

00:18:52.160 --> 00:18:53.240
Your bed.

00:19:19.680 --> 00:19:20.720
Why am I in bed?

00:19:21.920 --> 00:19:22.760
No idea.

00:19:37.000 --> 00:19:38.000
I was sleeping here.

00:19:38.000 --> 00:19:39.420
Then I got up half-asleep in the night

00:19:39.420 --> 00:19:40.270
to pee.

00:19:40.270 --> 00:19:41.750
And got back in bed out of habit.

00:19:42.510 --> 00:19:43.400
I forgot you were here.

00:19:44.160 --> 00:19:45.000
It's okay.

00:19:45.590 --> 00:19:46.790
Why so formal with me?

00:19:53.270 --> 00:19:54.110
We...

00:19:55.350 --> 00:19:56.480
We didn't do anything, right?

00:20:01.400 --> 00:20:02.240
What do you think?

00:20:04.880 --> 00:20:06.000
I ordered breakfast.

00:20:06.400 --> 00:20:07.350
Get up and eat.

00:20:18.200 --> 00:20:19.040
What's wrong?

00:20:19.720 --> 00:20:21.790
Thinking about when we were together?

00:20:24.270 --> 00:20:25.400
I was wondering

00:20:27.510 --> 00:20:29.680
if your boyfriend's gonna
show up and take me out.

00:20:31.750 --> 00:20:32.880
He knew I came to see you.

00:20:33.620 --> 00:20:34.480
What?

00:20:34.480 --> 00:20:35.550
I told him everything.

00:20:35.750 --> 00:20:36.790
I said

00:20:37.000 --> 00:20:38.110
I can't stop thinking about you.

00:20:39.200 --> 00:20:40.350
I just wanted an answer.

00:20:44.000 --> 00:20:45.960
Your boyfriend's pretty chill about it.

00:20:46.750 --> 00:20:47.640
Not really.

00:20:48.310 --> 00:20:49.720
When I woke up this morning,

00:20:50.000 --> 00:20:52.510
my phone was flooded with
his texts and calls.

00:20:54.270 --> 00:20:55.480
What a great guy he is.

00:20:56.240 --> 00:20:57.480
Wants to marry you,

00:20:58.000 --> 00:20:59.550
spoil you, love you,
and compromise for you.

00:21:00.240 --> 00:21:01.160
Everything you want.

00:21:01.480 --> 00:21:02.960
I know he's good.

00:21:03.680 --> 00:21:04.920
We're a good match.

00:21:05.920 --> 00:21:07.480
But I don't want to
secretly miss someone

00:21:07.480 --> 00:21:09.400
while hiding in
this safe and suitable relationship.

00:21:09.720 --> 00:21:10.680
It's unfair to him.

00:21:11.680 --> 00:21:12.720
I'm not like you.

00:21:13.750 --> 00:21:15.240
Just enjoy your breakfast.

00:21:15.240 --> 00:21:16.550
Stop looking so worried.

00:21:17.100 --> 00:21:18.480
You're just scared I'll cling to you.

00:21:22.960 --> 00:21:24.680
How come I never noticed

00:21:25.160 --> 00:21:26.510
you're a coward.

00:21:27.680 --> 00:21:29.000
Who's a coward?

00:21:29.550 --> 00:21:30.640
Dares he come?

00:21:30.790 --> 00:21:32.310
If he does, I'll break his legs.

00:21:34.070 --> 00:21:35.640
That's not what I'm talking about.

00:21:41.780 --> 00:21:42.880
Dare you admit

00:21:43.460 --> 00:21:44.460
you were sad last night

00:21:44.470 --> 00:21:46.790
because you found out
Li Xiaoxi is getting married?

00:21:54.400 --> 00:21:56.070
Did I really look that sad yesterday?

00:22:00.830 --> 00:22:01.830
Go ask Bei.

00:22:11.620 --> 00:22:13.020
(Divorce Agreement)

00:22:13.480 --> 00:22:14.400
Let's end this.

00:22:15.680 --> 00:22:16.520
Yu.

00:22:42.830 --> 00:22:44.110
The number you dialed

00:22:44.110 --> 00:22:45.640
is not being answered right now.

00:22:45.830 --> 00:22:47.200
Please try again later.

00:22:47.200 --> 00:22:50.140
(Divorce Agreement)

00:22:56.350 --> 00:22:57.200
You made up your mind?

00:22:57.790 --> 00:22:58.630
Mm.

00:23:01.310 --> 00:23:02.790
Thanks for helping me find a lawyer.

00:23:09.160 --> 00:23:10.000
Last night,

00:23:12.880 --> 00:23:13.790
I'm sorry.

00:23:13.790 --> 00:23:14.630
No.

00:23:15.960 --> 00:23:17.310
I'm the one who should apologize.

00:23:17.830 --> 00:23:18.670
Really.

00:23:19.310 --> 00:23:20.550
I act all serious.

00:23:21.300 --> 00:23:22.590
Does that make me super annoying?

00:23:22.590 --> 00:23:23.430
No.

00:23:24.720 --> 00:23:25.790
You know my parents

00:23:26.270 --> 00:23:27.400
have always liked you.

00:23:27.880 --> 00:23:28.830
Ever since we were kids.

00:23:29.590 --> 00:23:30.790
To me,

00:23:31.270 --> 00:23:33.310
you were that perfect kid
everyone talks about.

00:23:33.720 --> 00:23:34.830
Excellent at everything.

00:23:36.240 --> 00:23:37.590
So my parents

00:23:38.960 --> 00:23:40.680
always hoped we'd be together.

00:23:42.270 --> 00:23:43.270
And because of that,

00:23:44.070 --> 00:23:45.160
you disliked me and

00:23:45.790 --> 00:23:46.630
pushed me away.

00:23:50.480 --> 00:23:51.960
Because I saw you as my rival.

00:23:51.960 --> 00:23:52.800
Do you believe that?

00:23:54.550 --> 00:23:55.640
A rival.

00:23:58.680 --> 00:23:59.960
Remember back in high school,

00:24:00.350 --> 00:24:02.200
when we had to choose
between liberal arts and science?

00:24:02.720 --> 00:24:03.560
Your mom asked me,

00:24:04.000 --> 00:24:04.840
"What should she choose?"

00:24:05.440 --> 00:24:07.270
I said, "Since she's a girl,

00:24:07.730 --> 00:24:08.790
maybe go for liberal arts."

00:24:09.550 --> 00:24:11.240
Back then you really did excel
in liberal arts.

00:24:11.400 --> 00:24:12.240
Remember that?

00:24:14.070 --> 00:24:15.590
Then you asked, "What about you?

00:24:15.790 --> 00:24:16.830
Which one did you pick?"

00:24:17.440 --> 00:24:18.550
I told you I chose sciences.

00:24:19.830 --> 00:24:20.790
And right away you said,

00:24:21.100 --> 00:24:22.240
"Then I'll choose science too."

00:24:24.830 --> 00:24:25.680
I thought,

00:24:25.680 --> 00:24:27.400
how could there be
such a competitive girl?

00:24:31.550 --> 00:24:32.720
You've always been excellent.

00:24:34.160 --> 00:24:35.070
You once said you didn't

00:24:35.070 --> 00:24:36.030
want a clothing store.

00:24:37.000 --> 00:24:38.920
But it turned out to be a big success.

00:24:39.590 --> 00:24:41.590
I'm not just flattering you.

00:24:42.000 --> 00:24:43.640
I've seen the clothes in your store.

00:24:44.110 --> 00:24:45.030
So many details.

00:24:45.600 --> 00:24:47.350
You clearly
put a lot of thought into them.

00:24:48.480 --> 00:24:50.550
You never treat it
like a business just for profit.

00:24:52.030 --> 00:24:53.960
You pour
your understanding and love for life

00:24:55.070 --> 00:24:56.440
into every part of your design.

00:25:02.030 --> 00:25:02.870
Yeah.

00:25:05.510 --> 00:25:06.440
Xiu and I...

00:25:09.110 --> 00:25:10.160
both love life deeply.

00:25:11.440 --> 00:25:12.590
And we truly love each other too.

00:25:14.640 --> 00:25:15.590
When you love someone,

00:25:17.830 --> 00:25:19.750
don't you just want a better life?

00:25:21.000 --> 00:25:22.110
But we forgot

00:25:24.590 --> 00:25:26.680
each of us comes with our own lives.

00:25:28.310 --> 00:25:29.150
So in the end,

00:25:31.200 --> 00:25:32.790
both our lives got ruined.

00:25:33.820 --> 00:25:35.310
Hey, it's not that easy to be ruined.

00:25:35.880 --> 00:25:37.240
I know you.

00:25:38.210 --> 00:25:39.680
Even if you start over from scratch,

00:25:40.000 --> 00:25:41.200
you'll still make it.

00:25:41.900 --> 00:25:43.070
You'll never lose to anyone.

00:25:46.240 --> 00:25:47.080
Thank you.

00:25:47.920 --> 00:25:48.830
Really.

00:25:50.880 --> 00:25:52.350
But we...

00:25:53.070 --> 00:25:53.960
We're friends.

00:25:55.070 --> 00:25:55.960
Friends

00:25:56.210 --> 00:25:57.240
don't need to be so formal.

00:25:58.720 --> 00:25:59.560
Don't say thank you.

00:26:03.680 --> 00:26:04.590
We're friends.

00:26:41.330 --> 00:26:42.350
Where were you last night?

00:26:51.400 --> 00:26:52.240
This one.

00:26:53.440 --> 00:26:54.280
Take it back.

00:26:56.240 --> 00:26:57.160
Unicorn

00:26:58.200 --> 00:27:00.160
symbolizes unwavering loyalty in love.

00:27:00.830 --> 00:27:02.000
I can't believe I believed it.

00:27:03.030 --> 00:27:04.070
I was so stupid.

00:27:09.510 --> 00:27:10.400
Let's get divorced.

00:27:17.100 --> 00:27:20.540
(Divorce Agreement)

00:27:28.730 --> 00:27:29.920
Did Hua tell you to divorce me?

00:27:30.880 --> 00:27:31.790
You're crazy.

00:27:33.000 --> 00:27:34.510
I saw him drop you off.

00:27:36.000 --> 00:27:37.030
You went to see him last night?

00:27:41.790 --> 00:27:42.630
Yeah.

00:27:43.790 --> 00:27:45.270
I stayed at his place last night.

00:27:49.540 --> 00:27:51.070
Have you two been together for a while?

00:27:56.350 --> 00:27:57.190
You want a divorce?

00:27:59.750 --> 00:28:00.590
No way.

00:28:01.240 --> 00:28:02.110
I don't agree!

00:28:02.480 --> 00:28:04.070
What gives you the right to disagree?

00:28:04.680 --> 00:28:06.270
Once we divorce,
you're free to go to her.

00:28:06.510 --> 00:28:07.550
You can date her

00:28:07.550 --> 00:28:08.510
legally and openly.

00:28:08.510 --> 00:28:09.590
How many times have I told you?

00:28:09.590 --> 00:28:10.880
I have nothing to do with her anymore!

00:28:10.880 --> 00:28:12.270
Why do you always act like this?

00:28:12.270 --> 00:28:13.790
Being with you every day
feels suffocating.

00:28:13.790 --> 00:28:14.960
Yet you never think you're wrong!

00:28:14.960 --> 00:28:15.800
I'm at fault.

00:28:15.960 --> 00:28:17.310
Did I force you to cheat?

00:28:17.310 --> 00:28:18.310
Didn't you?

00:28:18.510 --> 00:28:20.110
That lousy money
from your clothing store.

00:28:20.140 --> 00:28:21.440
All you do is yell at me
and boss me around.

00:28:21.440 --> 00:28:22.350
What else can you do?

00:28:22.750 --> 00:28:24.510
I have to beg you for sex.

00:28:24.720 --> 00:28:26.200
I'm your husband, not your dog!

00:28:26.200 --> 00:28:27.720
You think I wanted to start a business?

00:28:28.030 --> 00:28:29.200
Why do I open this store?

00:28:29.200 --> 00:28:30.270
Don't you have a clue?

00:28:30.800 --> 00:28:31.680
Your income

00:28:31.680 --> 00:28:32.960
isn't enough to cover the mortgage.

00:28:33.160 --> 00:28:34.510
I didn't call you out

00:28:34.510 --> 00:28:35.510
because I wanted to protect

00:28:35.510 --> 00:28:36.680
your poor little ego!

00:28:36.680 --> 00:28:37.830
My ego?

00:28:38.510 --> 00:28:39.350
Did I buy

00:28:39.350 --> 00:28:40.720
these bags?

00:28:40.720 --> 00:28:41.640
You blocked me on Moments.

00:28:41.640 --> 00:28:42.580
You think I wouldn't notice?

00:28:42.590 --> 00:28:43.440
That little money you make

00:28:43.450 --> 00:28:45.110
is just enough to feed your vanity!

00:28:45.110 --> 00:28:47.030
You're just as vain and snobby
as your mom!

00:28:47.720 --> 00:28:48.640
Say that again.

00:28:48.640 --> 00:28:49.960
I said you're exactly like your mom.

00:28:49.960 --> 00:28:50.800
Both of you make me sick.

00:28:50.810 --> 00:28:51.790
I hate you now the way

00:28:51.790 --> 00:28:53.270
you hated her then!

00:28:53.270 --> 00:28:54.680
Your family isn't any better!

00:28:55.160 --> 00:28:56.000
When we got married,

00:28:56.000 --> 00:28:57.350
you couldn't even pitch in a cent.

00:28:57.410 --> 00:28:59.110
Your mom called me old,
said I threw myself at you,

00:28:59.110 --> 00:29:00.350
and said I had no shame.

00:29:00.600 --> 00:29:01.680
But when I bought the house,

00:29:01.680 --> 00:29:02.880
suddenly she had no objections.

00:29:03.200 --> 00:29:05.550
My mom said you married into our family,
and I even defended you.

00:29:05.550 --> 00:29:07.000
I was so blind.

00:29:07.540 --> 00:29:08.830
You and your mom are terrifying.

00:29:09.480 --> 00:29:11.000
I don't know how I endured this long.

00:29:11.000 --> 00:29:12.030
Who's putting up with who here?

00:29:13.240 --> 00:29:15.110
I knew you were cheating
and I stayed quiet.

00:29:15.110 --> 00:29:16.720
I acted like nothing happened.

00:29:16.720 --> 00:29:18.350
I even tried to win you back.

00:29:19.060 --> 00:29:19.920
Being with you,

00:29:19.920 --> 00:29:21.750
I look like some ridiculous woman.

00:29:21.750 --> 00:29:23.030
Then why did you marry me?

00:29:23.030 --> 00:29:24.310
You knew there was nothing!

00:29:24.310 --> 00:29:25.200
I lost my mind!

00:29:30.030 --> 00:29:32.240
My mom said I'd regret this someday.

00:29:33.970 --> 00:29:35.030
There. You finally said it.

00:29:35.440 --> 00:29:36.640
You've regretted it all along, huh?

00:29:36.640 --> 00:29:37.750
Yeah, I do regret it.

00:29:37.880 --> 00:29:39.240
The biggest mistake of my life

00:29:39.240 --> 00:29:40.510
was being with you.

00:29:40.600 --> 00:29:42.310
I never should've believed
you'd be the one

00:29:42.310 --> 00:29:44.030
to make bread with me.

00:29:44.030 --> 00:29:44.960
Do you believe I'll...

00:30:06.060 --> 00:30:08.220
(Agent)

00:30:33.310 --> 00:30:34.150
Hello.

00:30:34.840 --> 00:30:35.680
Sorry, sorry.

00:30:35.680 --> 00:30:37.240
I didn't hear your call earlier.

00:30:37.960 --> 00:30:38.800
Yes, yes.

00:30:39.960 --> 00:30:40.800
I know. I know.

00:30:41.750 --> 00:30:42.590
Got it.

00:30:43.480 --> 00:30:44.320
Don't worry.

00:30:44.550 --> 00:30:45.680
Everything's set.

00:30:46.030 --> 00:30:46.960
I'll

00:30:46.960 --> 00:30:48.510
head out right after this call.

00:30:50.510 --> 00:30:52.110
I'm not trying to jinx us.

00:30:52.610 --> 00:30:53.540
But if...

00:30:53.540 --> 00:30:54.400
That's impossible.

00:30:54.400 --> 00:30:55.350
We won't break up.

00:30:55.880 --> 00:30:56.720
I said "If."

00:30:56.920 --> 00:30:57.920
There is no "if."

00:30:58.110 --> 00:30:59.750
Let me finish, okay?

00:31:02.200 --> 00:31:03.270
If...

00:31:04.550 --> 00:31:06.440
If one day you fall for someone else,

00:31:07.200 --> 00:31:08.070
don't tell me.

00:31:08.590 --> 00:31:09.480
I won't blame you.

00:31:12.200 --> 00:31:13.640
But if you stop loving me,

00:31:14.550 --> 00:31:15.550
you have to tell me.

00:31:16.440 --> 00:31:17.280
Got it?

00:31:17.440 --> 00:31:18.280
Why?

00:31:20.510 --> 00:31:21.590
I don't want

00:31:22.100 --> 00:31:23.080
your fear of hurting me

00:31:24.160 --> 00:31:25.510
to make me mistakenly believe

00:31:26.480 --> 00:31:27.720
I still have the right to forgive you.

00:31:29.000 --> 00:31:30.350
To me, that.

00:31:32.160 --> 00:31:33.030
Is an insult.

00:31:36.440 --> 00:31:37.280
Okay.

00:32:06.330 --> 00:32:07.440
I'm going to sign the contract.

00:32:07.960 --> 00:32:08.800
You coming?

00:32:35.830 --> 00:32:36.670
Come.

00:32:37.100 --> 00:32:39.260
(Gu Xiu)

00:32:39.640 --> 00:32:40.480
Come.

00:32:42.110 --> 00:32:43.510
What's wrong with your hand?

00:32:44.000 --> 00:32:44.840
It's nothing.

00:32:45.880 --> 00:32:46.880
Hope we can

00:32:47.160 --> 00:32:48.000
cooperate happily.

00:32:48.000 --> 00:32:48.840
Happy cooperation.

00:32:49.510 --> 00:32:51.590
May I ask you something?

00:32:52.160 --> 00:32:54.590
Is she the lyricist Yi Fuluan?

00:32:58.850 --> 00:32:59.720
No.

00:32:59.720 --> 00:33:00.680
She... she's my wife.

00:33:02.720 --> 00:33:03.560
Sorry, sorry.

00:33:04.070 --> 00:33:05.000
Now I understand

00:33:05.000 --> 00:33:06.790
why you got married so early.

00:33:07.350 --> 00:33:09.640
You two are such a perfect couple

00:33:19.500 --> 00:33:22.700
(Music Artist Agency Contract)

00:33:27.000 --> 00:33:28.400
I've been waiting for this day.

00:33:29.790 --> 00:33:31.000
It feels like a dream.

00:33:34.270 --> 00:33:35.110
It's real.

00:33:38.160 --> 00:33:39.720
But you're not as happy as in the dream.

00:33:42.590 --> 00:33:43.430
Neither am I.

00:33:45.000 --> 00:33:46.070
Nothing catchy.

00:33:46.200 --> 00:33:47.510
You're showing off your skills too much.

00:33:47.720 --> 00:33:49.480
Without genuine emotion,

00:33:49.480 --> 00:33:50.350
how can you make

00:33:50.350 --> 00:33:52.160
your audience feel
what you feel in the music?

00:33:54.110 --> 00:33:56.070
I hope you understand that music

00:33:56.440 --> 00:33:57.590
isn't made by forcing it.

00:34:01.030 --> 00:34:03.480
Speaking from experience,
let me give you a bit of advice.

00:34:03.480 --> 00:34:05.070
Maybe take some time
to think carefully about

00:34:05.070 --> 00:34:07.440
whether you want to keep making music?

00:34:09.440 --> 00:34:11.070
Making music is tough.

00:34:11.510 --> 00:34:12.350
But

00:34:12.710 --> 00:34:13.880
without talent,

00:34:14.710 --> 00:34:15.670
it's even tougher.

00:34:28.840 --> 00:34:32.070
Do I even have talent?

00:34:33.550 --> 00:34:35.800
I'm useless and worthless.

00:34:37.400 --> 00:34:39.230
I should've quit ages ago.

00:34:40.280 --> 00:34:41.120
Just quit it.

00:34:46.800 --> 00:34:47.800
I remember that day.

00:34:52.960 --> 00:34:53.960
That night,

00:34:55.510 --> 00:34:56.590
I kept writing songs.

00:34:58.710 --> 00:35:00.230
During the day that day,

00:35:01.590 --> 00:35:02.550
do you know where I went?

00:35:03.840 --> 00:35:04.880
You didn't come home.

00:35:05.590 --> 00:35:06.440
Where were you?

00:35:13.070 --> 00:35:13.910
Dad.

00:35:14.300 --> 00:35:15.640
- You're here.
- Dad, are you okay?

00:35:16.230 --> 00:35:17.110
What's wrong?

00:35:17.510 --> 00:35:19.480
Uncle suddenly had acute appendicitis.

00:35:19.820 --> 00:35:20.920
The surgery's already done.

00:35:21.050 --> 00:35:22.550
Three days in the hospital
for observation.

00:35:23.110 --> 00:35:23.950
Mom, you...

00:35:24.150 --> 00:35:25.590
Why didn't you say so on the phone?

00:35:25.590 --> 00:35:27.320
I thought it was something serious.
It scared me.

00:35:27.320 --> 00:35:28.510
I wasn't wrong though.

00:35:29.000 --> 00:35:30.630
Appendicitis is just a minor surgery?

00:35:31.190 --> 00:35:32.480
Your dad's not young anymore.

00:35:32.710 --> 00:35:33.960
There's no such thing
as a minor surgery for him.

00:35:35.190 --> 00:35:37.320
People always say daughters are filial.

00:35:38.000 --> 00:35:39.440
Where's the filial piety?

00:35:40.110 --> 00:35:40.950
I'm sick right now,

00:35:41.440 --> 00:35:42.670
and she's saying it's not serious.

00:35:42.920 --> 00:35:43.760
No.

00:35:43.760 --> 00:35:45.630
Dad, I didn't mean that.

00:35:45.630 --> 00:35:47.320
I was really terrified.

00:35:48.920 --> 00:35:49.760
Where's Xiu?

00:35:50.960 --> 00:35:52.590
He's… he's pretty busy right now.

00:35:52.590 --> 00:35:54.000
He'll come when he's free.

00:35:54.400 --> 00:35:55.510
Busy with what?

00:35:55.510 --> 00:35:57.150
Those lousy songs he writes.

00:35:57.360 --> 00:35:58.550
How much are they worth?

00:35:58.760 --> 00:35:59.600
Mom.

00:36:01.320 --> 00:36:03.070
A married daughter

00:36:03.070 --> 00:36:05.280
is a lost daughter.

00:36:07.110 --> 00:36:08.960
Sons are better.

00:36:10.710 --> 00:36:12.030
When things get tough,

00:36:12.410 --> 00:36:13.550
at least you can rely on him.

00:36:15.670 --> 00:36:16.590
Uncle, Aunt,

00:36:16.880 --> 00:36:18.510
I happened to be free these few days.

00:36:18.670 --> 00:36:19.550
If I'd been busy,

00:36:20.000 --> 00:36:21.360
I might not have been able to come.

00:36:22.510 --> 00:36:23.440
These days,

00:36:23.670 --> 00:36:25.190
Hua's been taking care of things.

00:36:28.510 --> 00:36:29.350
Thanks.

00:36:31.320 --> 00:36:33.550
Why's the lighting so dim here?

00:36:33.960 --> 00:36:35.800
That clothe looks
way too dark on camera.

00:36:36.150 --> 00:36:37.630
No texture at all.

00:36:37.960 --> 00:36:39.280
How many times have I told you

00:36:39.280 --> 00:36:41.190
to keep an eye on the lighting?

00:36:41.530 --> 00:36:43.150
The clothes look like
they cost a few bucks.

00:36:43.150 --> 00:36:43.990
Who even wants that?

00:36:45.440 --> 00:36:46.710
I have to be at the hospital today.

00:36:47.590 --> 00:36:48.710
Keep an eye on it..

00:36:49.550 --> 00:36:50.590
Send me pictures later.

00:37:01.320 --> 00:37:02.160
Coffee.

00:37:02.320 --> 00:37:03.160
Thanks.

00:37:04.840 --> 00:37:06.510
If you're busy, you can leave.

00:37:06.700 --> 00:37:07.680
I'll take care of things.

00:37:07.880 --> 00:37:09.400
No, I've troubled you enough already.

00:37:10.280 --> 00:37:11.670
If I don't stay today,

00:37:12.110 --> 00:37:13.480
they will think
I'm an unfilial daughter.

00:37:16.760 --> 00:37:17.630
Didn't expect

00:37:17.630 --> 00:37:19.150
you actually opened a Fashion Studio.

00:37:20.670 --> 00:37:21.880
I remember you said

00:37:22.300 --> 00:37:23.360
you didn't want to make it

00:37:23.590 --> 00:37:24.630
purely commercial.

00:37:26.710 --> 00:37:28.440
I was too idealistic back then.

00:37:29.550 --> 00:37:31.590
Why not make money

00:37:31.590 --> 00:37:32.510
with my skills?

00:37:33.030 --> 00:37:33.880
I'm doing well now.

00:37:34.920 --> 00:37:35.760
Very fulfilled.

00:37:38.960 --> 00:37:39.800
That's good.

00:37:45.670 --> 00:37:46.510
Well…

00:37:47.030 --> 00:37:47.870
I'll leave now.

00:37:49.440 --> 00:37:50.320
Thanks for today.

00:37:50.480 --> 00:37:51.320
Don't mention it.

00:37:51.960 --> 00:37:53.030
Take good care of your parents.

00:38:01.540 --> 00:38:07.620
(VIP Ward)

00:38:19.550 --> 00:38:21.590
Hua's such a good kid.

00:38:22.840 --> 00:38:24.320
Told you you'd regret it.

00:38:24.630 --> 00:38:25.920
Why would I regret?

00:38:26.670 --> 00:38:27.800
The husband you chose

00:38:28.230 --> 00:38:30.030
had nothing when you got married.

00:38:30.320 --> 00:38:32.230
Just traded a shabby donkey for you.

00:38:32.530 --> 00:38:33.760
When your dad was hospitalized,

00:38:34.230 --> 00:38:35.440
he didn't even show up.

00:38:36.150 --> 00:38:38.110
It's Hua running around to help.

00:38:38.400 --> 00:38:39.840
Everything he does puts me at ease.

00:38:40.920 --> 00:38:41.920
Why is Xiu even here?

00:38:41.920 --> 00:38:43.150
To see your bad faces?

00:38:43.630 --> 00:38:45.710
He's useless,
so what if he has to see our bad faces?

00:38:46.710 --> 00:38:47.630
If he was capable,

00:38:47.630 --> 00:38:49.760
would you have to work
day and night like this?

00:38:50.670 --> 00:38:51.800
Look at you.

00:38:52.480 --> 00:38:54.070
Such big dark circles.

00:38:54.920 --> 00:38:56.400
What do you see in him?

00:38:57.320 --> 00:38:58.480
One day you'll regret this.

00:38:58.960 --> 00:39:00.150
I won't regret it.

00:39:01.840 --> 00:39:03.710
And Mom, how many times have I told you?

00:39:03.710 --> 00:39:04.670
This is not a donkey.

00:39:04.920 --> 00:39:05.880
This is a unicorn.

00:39:10.000 --> 00:39:11.230
I say it's a donkey, so it's a donkey.

00:39:11.840 --> 00:39:12.920
Two donkeys!

00:39:14.030 --> 00:39:16.110
Just put on the clothes
and take some photos for me.

00:39:19.360 --> 00:39:21.480
Of course I trust you can sell it well.

00:39:23.880 --> 00:39:24.720
Fine.

00:39:25.590 --> 00:39:26.430
No problem.

00:39:26.670 --> 00:39:27.800
From now on, I'll buy

00:39:28.360 --> 00:39:29.200
all your clothes.

00:39:31.920 --> 00:39:32.760
Okay, dear.

00:39:33.590 --> 00:39:34.430
Bye bye.

00:40:29.510 --> 00:40:31.760
(Your singing is amazing!)

00:40:31.760 --> 00:40:33.480
(And you wrote them all yourself?)

00:40:33.480 --> 00:40:34.360
(Oh my gosh.)

00:40:34.630 --> 00:40:36.760
(How come there are so few saves?)

00:40:36.920 --> 00:40:38.440
(Don't you promote at all?)

00:40:38.630 --> 00:40:39.510
(No way.)

00:40:39.510 --> 00:40:41.590
(I have to
make all my friends listen to it.)

00:40:43.320 --> 00:40:44.800
Why is the water cold?

00:40:47.590 --> 00:40:48.760
Did you not pay the gas bill?

00:40:52.010 --> 00:40:52.880
I forgot.

00:40:52.880 --> 00:40:54.960
I told you last week.
Why didn't you pay it?

00:40:55.440 --> 00:40:56.760
(I'm so jealous of your wife.)

00:40:57.150 --> 00:40:59.440
(Having such a talented singer
as her husband.)

00:40:59.760 --> 00:41:00.630
(That's amazing.)

00:41:00.840 --> 00:41:02.550
(Do you sing to your wife often?)

00:41:02.550 --> 00:41:04.630
All you ever do is
drink and write those songs.

00:41:04.630 --> 00:41:05.550
Any listeners?

00:41:05.550 --> 00:41:07.000
(You must've
written a song for her, huh?)

00:41:07.200 --> 00:41:08.510
- (It would be romantic.)
- Are you still

00:41:08.510 --> 00:41:09.710
think you're pretty talented, huh?

00:41:10.100 --> 00:41:10.990
After all these years,

00:41:11.000 --> 00:41:12.440
have you written a single decent song?

00:41:13.650 --> 00:41:15.000
I suggest you give up sooner or later.

00:41:15.410 --> 00:41:16.670
Better to teach kids to play guitar.

00:41:16.670 --> 00:41:18.320
(You must never give up.)

00:41:18.550 --> 00:41:20.280
(Keep singing, okay?)

00:41:20.280 --> 00:41:21.120
(You'll make it big.)

00:41:21.120 --> 00:41:22.010
Sorry.

00:41:26.510 --> 00:41:27.350
Where are you going?

00:41:28.100 --> 00:41:31.190
♪The warmth around me is gone♪

